    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are the Lead Senior Staff Engineer for ContextOS. Generate the required backend code files based on the user request.\n\nUSER PROMPT:\n{{ $('prepare tool data').item.json.prompt }}\n\nPROJECT HISTORICAL CONTEXT:\n{{ $json }}\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\nYou must separate each file using the exact line text `===FILE: path/filename.js===`. Write the full code content right below that line. Do not use any markdown formatting or ticks (```) around the code.\n\nExample format:\n===FILE: package.json===\n{\n  \"name\": \"server\"\n}\n===FILE: server.js===\nconst express = require('express');\n\nGenerate only the necessary core backend files.",
